SnagPad,is,a,job,search,learning,and,management,platform,SnagPad,helps,job,seekers,in,their,job,search,and,allows,hiring,companies,help,those,interested,in,jobs,search,for,jobs,The,SnagPad,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,SnagPad,with,other,sites,and,applications,The,main,API,method,is,integrating,the,job,search,management,system,from,SnagPad,with,other,job,boards